            <title>[CASSANDRA-17547] Documentation from Partition Denylist Lost in Document Migration + Minor Fixes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17547</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The documentation added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-12106&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-12106&lt;/a&gt; went missing when the documents were migrated to the new format. We just need to bring the doc back. Along with this fix there are a couple minor edits to make to the document itself to correct the examples.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
