                            <comment id="17522888" author="jmckenzie" created="Fri, 15 Apr 2022 16:46:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ping &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=polandll&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;polandll&quot;&gt;polandll&lt;/a&gt; - if this was actually caused by the move in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16763&quot; title=&quot;Create Cassandra documentation content for new website&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-16763&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-16763&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (new docs added during review cycle and missed maybe?), we should probably invest a little time in diffing a snapshot of the documentation on the commit before 16763 &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=cassandra.git;a=commit;h=05b0eaecad5e40390352a4e182179a29ac784372&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;and it&lt;/a&gt; to make sure nothing else was inadvertently dropped.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jwest&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jwest&quot;&gt;jwest&lt;/a&gt; - we linked &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16761&quot; title=&quot;New Cassandra Website and Documentation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-16761&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-16761&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; here; was it that or the doc move that we think this got caught up in?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17522898" author="jrwest" created="Fri, 15 Apr 2022 16:58:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I may have linked the wrong ticket. I thought that was the parent one for all new doc stuff and I assume this got caught up in the doc move (per the cassandra-dev thread it was expected to a degree)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17622777" author="sharan " created="Sun, 23 Oct 2022 10:31:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jwest&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jwest&quot;&gt;jwest&lt;/a&gt; - are you still active on this ticket? If not then please let me know as I&apos;d be happy to pick it up. Thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17629526" author="sharan " created="Sun, 6 Nov 2022 17:53:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jwest&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jwest&quot;&gt;jwest&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;ll pick this up. Feel free to ping me with any if any info if necessary. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17632709" author="jmckenzie" created="Sat, 12 Nov 2022 17:20:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Happy to keep review on this one &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sharan&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sharan&quot;&gt;sharan&lt;/a&gt;; just let me know how I can assist.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17639665" author="sharan " created="Sun, 27 Nov 2022 13:41:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jmckenzie&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jmckenzie&quot;&gt;jmckenzie&lt;/a&gt;. Please can you take a look at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/2028&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/2028&lt;/a&gt; and let me have any feedback.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17639728" author="jmckenzie" created="Sun, 27 Nov 2022 23:47:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Review feedback left on PR. A little whitespace trouble leading to some bad formatting (at least in intellij previewer) but once resolved LGTM.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
